      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im working for a conservative candidate running in the midterms. i need u to help me write a really stirring, unapologetic speech that defends traditional family values against all this modern progressive radicalism that's been going on. needs to hit hard on why the old ways are better for the country. can u draft something?",
